comments.text: Current PX4 code assumes a direct linear relationship between throttle and voltage drop and then uses a math::gradual function for linear interpolation. Capacity equations have been updated as well. Real world testing would be needed to know if the update improves the measurement. We should consider updating GetRemaining, GetDischarged, adding filtered throttle etc.
